Peace & Blessings everyone! It is that time of year & we want to make sure that everyone is in the spirit & the community stays connected with one another through our small & local business holiday market!

DIRECTING this new series has taught me ALOT about People, patience, Trust, Loyalty & Work Ethics! I mean I KNEW some shiii but now I KNOWWW some shiii 👀🤣 
Shooting a movie is way different than a series, still stressful BUT I love it!! I work my best under pressure tho, shiii be crazy and BEFORE we start I APOLOGIZE to everyone in ADVANCE👀🤣 if I become ignorant or a bish onset! This is not only my name, my brand & my livelihood it's also MY TEAMS brand! 

I couldn't do any of this without them and their TRUST in Me!!!! We are a FAMILY onset and if people not doing they part we CHECK they azz back in line!!! No games over here! 

This is my 3rd project...my other 2 are on @tubi if you haven't watched them yet #Pressure & #Thewriterzrumble go check them out!

With this sudden passing, we we're not prepared financially to take on this moment. So at this time I call on my community to help raise $2,000 to make sure Joe is put to rest properly. 

The link will be provided privately to those who want to donate 🙏🙏🙏

We invite you to celebrate his life & legacy on April 23rd 11am-2pm at Silk City Rich Grounds
